  EffectDiscription_ENG: "When you would play this Digimon, you may trash 7 or more
    digivolution cards from the bottom of 1 of your [Mother D-Reaper]s to set this
    Digimon's play cost to 0.\uFF1CRush\uFF1E (This Digimon can attack the turn it
    comes into play.) [When Attacking] You may place 2 [ADR-02 Searcher]s from your
    trash under this Digimon in any order as its bottom digivolution cards to unsuspend
    this Digimon."
